name: MC Escher
description:
Portrait of one of my favourite artists.

It's an AI portraiture technique I developed which uses an underlying photo to guide the text to image generation process.  

In this case a photo of Escher was transformed with the prompt 'in the style of Escher', in effect it's Escher 'painting' himself in a self portrait.

This piece convinced me with little doubt that we are now close to Picasso with AI art. 


Made with Text to Image synthesis (CLIP & VQGan)
